BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:📅 GO Fest 2026 Sunday Raid Makeup
DTSTART;TZID=Europe/Brussels:20260726T100000
DTEND;TZID=Europe/Brussels:20260726T190000
DTSTAMP:20260720T083936Z
UID:2026-07-26T10:00:00+02:00--6207751393065074531@leekduck-calendar
DESCRIPTION:We previously announced a special GO Fest 2026: Global Sunday 
 raid event in select regions. Upon further investigation\, we have found t
 hat the impact of technical issues related to raids was more widespread th
 an initially thought. Therefore\, we will expand the event globally to inc
 lude all Trainers. The event will take place on Sunday\, July 26\, 2026\, 
 from 10:00 a.m. to 7:00 p.m. local time.\n\nAdditionally\, we appreciate y
 our extended patience as we work through these updates. As a token of our 
 gratitude and sincere apology for the confusion we have caused\, we have i
 ncreased the number of free Raid Passes from 9 to 12 for this event.\n\nAs
  compensation for a technical issue that prevented some Trainers from join
 ing Raid Battles during Pokémon GO Fest 2026: Global\, a special Sunday r
 aid makeup event will be held on July 26\, 2026 from 10 am to 7 pm local t
 ime.\n\nRaid Bosses featured during the original Sunday of GO Fest 2026: G
 lobal—including Mega Mewtwo Y Super Mega Raids—will appear!\n\nMore in
 fo: https://leekduck.com/events/pokemon-go-fest-2026-global-sunday-raid-ma
 keup/\n\nData from LeekDuck.com
LOCATION:Pokemon GO
URL:https://leekduck.com/events/pokemon-go-fest-2026-global-sunday-raid-ma
 keup/
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Reminder: 📅 GO Fest 2026 Sunday Raid Makeup starts in 2 ho
 urs
TRIGGER:-PT2H
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
